[metadata]

Name:Test - Macro Replay - Pili-Pala Architect
URL:https://www.cardforge.org

Goal:Win

Turns:1

Difficulty:Rare

Description:Test puzzle for replaying a mana loop from the commander combo list: Pili-Pala plus Grand Architect. First use Grand Architect to make Pili-Pala blue. Then record one cycle that taps Pili-Pala for Grand Architect's artifact-only mana and untaps Pili-Pala to add one mana of any color. Repeat to build enough mana, then cast Walking Ballista large enough to defeat the opponent.

